  "description": "A vibrant hummingbird hovers near a bright orange and reddish-brown flower stalk. The hummingbird is mid-flight, wings outstretched, with a greenish-blue body and a dark head. The flower stalk is composed of many small, tubular blooms, densely packed together. The background is a soft, muted brown, creating a bokeh effect that highlights the subject. The lighting is natural and diffused, capturing the details of both the bird and the flower.",
